data.description: Fantastic home with 5 bedrooms and private back yard. Open concept with a formal dining and living area. Lots of light and bonus room upstairs for the kids to play while the main suite is on the main level. Guest bedroom with nearby bath allows guests to come and go as they like. Don't miss this. Perfect condition and well loved home ready for new owners to move right in.
